Detailed Description

Typedef Documentation

typedef struct HSIHeader_MCB_t HSIHeader_MCB

HSI Header MCB.

This is the master control block of the HSI Header module.

typedef struct HSIHeaderId_Track_t HSIHeaderId_Track

HSI Identifier Tracker.

The structure is used to track the allocation of track identifiers. It is possible to have multiple sessions and each of these sessions need to have a unique track identifier allocated to it.
